Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:05.38,Main_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,La delegazione del Regno delle bestie Eurazania
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:09.11,Main_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,è giunta a Tempest per ordine del Re demone Callion.
